      • destroyContact

        ContactDestructionStatus destroyContact(PersonalDataContactDestructionRequest purgeRequest)
        Given a purge request destroy the contact on the purge request. The status of the purge request must be updated upon completion.
        Parameters:
        purgeRequest - of contact to be destroyed
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if status returned is TC_NEW

      • translateABUIDToPublicIDs

        java.util.List<java.lang.String> translateABUIDToPublicIDs(java.lang.String addressBookUID)
        Returns a list of contact publicIDs that have the addressBookUID. Most apps should return a list of one.
        Parameters:
        addressBookUID - of the contact to translate
        Returns:
        List of contact publicIDs that have the addressBookUID

      • doesContactWithPublicIDExist

        boolean doesContactWithPublicIDExist(java.lang.String publicID)
        Returns true if the publicID can be found in the app contact table.
        Parameters:
        publicID - of the contact
        Returns:
        true if the contact exists; false otherwise

      • translatePublicIDtoABUID

        java.lang.String translatePublicIDtoABUID(java.lang.String publicID)
        Returns an ABUID that corresponds to a publicID.
        Parameters:
        publicID - of the contact to translate
        Returns:
        ABUID that corresponds to a publicID if exists otherwise null
